de.jannlab.generator

Interface NetGenerator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LSTMGenerator, MLPGenerator, NetCoreGenerator, RNNGenerator

    public interface NetGenerator
    This interface defines what a NetGenerator must be albe to. On one hand this is to clear the inner model, and on other hand this is a method for generation of networks.

    Author:
    Sebastian Otte
